{"type": "article", "id": 9781, "title": "Disney & Vans 联名 Young at Heart 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-20T07:12:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235425xY2bSwpJ0d1rnP3m.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Disney 最近与 Vans 推出了一个新的联名系列，这个名为 “Young at Heart” 的系列在风格上和其名字一样动感十足，他们把 Disney 经典的卡通形象，如米老鼠，唐老鸭，维尼小熊等印制在了 Vans 经典的“一脚蹬”以及书包，帆布鞋，袜子等产品上面，营造出浓浓的夏日可爱风。这个联名系列将在 6 月正式登陆 Vans 全球指定店铺。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052354239lazg58n2ZIftsdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235423MnFgk3rAotSXCEvP.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235424rAxDptK0bsTwfPeg.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235425pqlOvnwxsCMuDEmR.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}